and that was the hardest part.

288
00:34:01,407 --> 00:34:04,041
Every single time
i thought I knew something
or learned anything I...

289
00:34:10,181 --> 00:34:11,314
...didn't.

290
00:34:13,584 --> 00:34:17,020
