347
00:42:19,904 --> 00:42:21,538
-Goodnight.
-Goodnight, Nia.

348
00:43:06,283 --> 00:43:07,650
He knows.

349
00:43:11,455 --> 00:43:12,956
What are we going to do?

350
00:43:19,496 --> 00:43:21,064
We have to stay away
from each other.

351
00:43:24,602 --> 00:43:25,435
I can't...

352
00:43:26,203 --> 00:43:28,504
...stay away from you.
