388
00:47:45,229 --> 00:47:47,063
If you think about it,
we're kind of like preachers.

389
00:47:48,198 --> 00:47:49,699
Where did you study?

390
00:47:49,701 --> 00:47:49,699
I'm self-taught.

391
00:47:49,701 --> 00:47:53,069
I've always drawn pictures
