441
00:51:38,462 --> 00:51:39,195
Of course.

442
00:52:35,886 --> 00:52:37,820
Silas, you made it.

443
00:52:39,055 --> 00:52:40,589
Oh, this is great.
I'm glad you're here.

444
00:52:40,591 --> 00:52:43,792
Everybody, this is Silas.
